fathom id: NXCLHKXQ

# BunPress VitePress-Compatible Blocks & Templates Implementation Plan

## Overview
Implement all VitePress markdown blocks and containers as reusable `.stx` templates in `src/templates/blocks/`, ensuring full VitePress compatibility with proper styling and functionality.

## Progress Summary

### Completed Phases
- ✅ **Phase 1**: Inline Formatting (17/17 tests passing)
- ✅ **Phase 2**: Custom Containers (12/12 tests passing)
- ✅ **Phase 3**: GitHub-Flavored Alerts (10/10 tests passing)
- ✅ **Phase 4**: Advanced Code Blocks (83/83 tests passing)
- ✅ **Phase 5**: Content Features (68/71 tests passing, 3 known edge cases)
- ✅ **Phase 6**: File Inclusion (25/25 tests passing - 100% ✅)
- ✅ **Phase 6.3**: Comprehensive Documentation (~2000+ lines)
- ⚠️ **Phase 8**: Link & Image Enhancements (8/10 tests passing, 2 known limitations)

### Test Statistics
- **Total Tests Passing:** 223/228 (97.8% success rate) 🎉
- **Total Assertions:** 566 validated behaviors
- **Known Limitations:** 5 edge cases documented (acceptable for production)
- **Test Coverage:** All core functionality comprehensively tested
- **Latest Fix:** Markdown region inclusion regex corrected - all Phase 6 tests passing
- **Latest Addition:** Phase 8 external links and image lazy loading (partial implementation)

### Documentation Statistics
- **New Documentation Files:** 5 major files created
- **Updated Documentation Files:** 3 files significantly enhanced
- **Total Documentation Added:** ~2000+ lines
- **Coverage:** 100% of implemented features documented

### Features Implemented (All VitePress-Compatible)
1. ✅ Inline formatting (bold, italic, strikethrough, sub/sup, mark)
2. ✅ Custom containers (info, tip, warning, danger, details, raw)
3. ✅ GitHub alerts (note, tip, important, warning, caution)
4. ✅ Code line highlighting, line numbers, focus, diffs, errors/warnings
5. ✅ Code groups with tabs
6. ✅ Code imports from files (line ranges, regions)
7. ✅ Inline TOC with [[toc]] macro
8. ✅ Custom header anchors
9. ✅ Emoji support (150+ shortcodes)
10. ✅ Inline badges (4 types)
11. ✅ Markdown file inclusion (recursive, line ranges, regions)
12. ⚠️ External links (target="_blank", rel attributes, icons - 80% working)
13. ⚠️ Image lazy loading (loading="lazy" attribute - 80% working)

